CUBRID Code Review Tool
=====================================

1. Make Code Review
modify the code then
cd [src_root_directory] to change directory to source directory.
mkcreview -o [issue_number].creview
to make code review file.


2. Show changes as external diff tool (WinMerge or meld)
install diff tool
and open a .creview file in code_review (shell or batch file)

If you are using Windows OS, you need to have compression utilities. (gzip and tar)
http://www.gzip.org/
http://www.gnu.org/software/tar/


3. Download Diff Tools
http://winmerge.org/
http://meld.sourceforge.net/
